chaft und Kultur ein und enthält eine ausführliche Bibliographie.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 7aHISTORY / Asia / China.2bisacsh1 aGall, Lothar, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHölkeskamp, Karl-Joachim, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPatzold, Steffen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAsian Studies Contemporary Collection eBook Packagez978311064982608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2017 Part 1z978311076249508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2017z9783110547764oZDB-23-DEG0 cEPUBz97831103965600 cprintz978311035530740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311035532140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110355321423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110355321/original  a978-3-11-064982-6  Asian Studies Contemporary Collection eBook Package  a978-3-11-071954-3  DG Plus eBook-Package 2017b2017  a978-3-11-076249-5  DG Plus DeG Package 2017 Part 1b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DEGb2017  aZDB-23-DGGb2017